snippet.title: Dreams in the Witch House [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
Wishlist Dreams in the Witch House on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1902850/Dreams_in_the_Witch_House/

Coming out on February 16th, 2023 on Steam and GOG.com.

Step into the madness and unravel the mystery! The highly anticipated adventure game based on H.P. Lovecraft's "The Dreams in the Witch House" is finally coming to haunt your screens on February 16th. Get ready to experience an old-school adventure with a twist of RPG elements and an estimated playtime so long, you'll forget what reality is.

The wait is almost over, mark your calendars, lock your doors and get ready to face the unknown. See you in the witch house! 🔮🏚️
